<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ゲーム選択</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .game-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    .game-list a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    .game-list a:hover {
      background-color: #555;
    }
    .back {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #0077cc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>🎮 ゲームを選択してください</h1>

  <div class="game-list">
    <a href="index.html">🧩 ボール落とし</a>
  </div>

  <a href="../index.html" class="back">← ポートフォリオに戻る</a>

</body>
</html>
